{"tid":1403203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃 大 仙 真 係 一 個 好 地 方！！！","createTime":"2019-08-03T18:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T00:01:55.000Z","uid":78007,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"27a905ed126c8762844ea40043847ef4ce597b60","tid":1403203,"uid":78007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"發夢去黃大仙睇樓<br />\n<br />\n先講警署，隔離大大個警察宿舍，可以同警察老婆仔女交流下，玩下幻彩詠香江<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你隔離大大條龍翔道，超容易做到be water！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n龍翔道上面條橋又可以觀戰、嗌口號、左可以望到警署，中間可以望到龍翔道交通情況，右邊可以望到沙田坳道，容易傳達訊息...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面有個慈雲山，有咩事就兄弟爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有竹園、鳳德呢啲大邨，正到爆炸<br />\n<br />\n慈雲山個警署又荒廢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n交通方便，街坊隨叫隨到，左鄰右里互相關心，一齊返屋企，唔講都唔知原來我屋企果層都有手足，咁就識到新朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d47c164873d42e926f64bbaa412ec95dca5546","tid":1403203,"uid":249789,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:04:12.000Z","msg":"推！好撚興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820ca6247dd8c84c4889c3d2eb001b4c43f0c930","tid":1403203,"uid":26813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">sorry借位宣傳<br />\n幫手推俾前線手足睇！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">！！！實用post！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［前線路障快閃團］簡易快速拆鐵欄攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400592</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fd988d7f6d5649e61be63e6473d83841429eb959","tid":1403203,"uid":78007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"推！地產商快啲發展下黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3173ad8aafea067d96f118c584a45c17d075a8","tid":1403203,"uid":78007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e2e64d69bcc119ad87c97ca7187e60f5cde8d0","tid":1403203,"uid":78007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8332630e934a8c6ad98e477919600c4e01e6d3","tid":1403203,"uid":285973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:18:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9b35bd61db56826869fa694e59d28eafbb64097a","tid":1403203,"uid":113250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fSb69fU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfSb69fU.jpg&h=370ef44e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e035bfb3b2e92f065b8cda494c644458bad8b48","tid":1403203,"uid":103325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:20:42.000Z","msg":"幻彩詠香江 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89226faa2bb5473acc1d622c13721583128d152","tid":1403203,"uid":78007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e035bfb3b2e92f065b8cda494c644458bad8b48","tid":1403203,"uid":103325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci